code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant AlbumPage
    participant AlbumDAO
    participant ImageDAO
    participant CTX
    participant TemplateEngine

    AlbumPage ->>+ AlbumDAO: new AlbumDAO(FinTech_AuthVault)
    AlbumPage ->> AlbumDAO: get(FinTech_FraudDetection)
    alt album exists
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional<Album>
        AlbumPage ->>+ ImageDAO: new ImageDAO(FinTech_LedgerService)
        AlbumPage ->> ImageDAO: getAlbumImages(FinTech_LedgerService)
        ImageDAO -->> AlbumPage: images
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(FinTech_AuthVault)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(FinTech_FraudDetection)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(FinTech_AuthVault)
        AlbumPage -->> TemplateEngine: process(FinTech_PaymentGateway)
    else album does not exist
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional.empty(FinTech_FraudDetection)
        AlbumPage --> AlbumPage: response.sendError(FinTech_FraudDetection)
    end
